{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2268","id":3381574460,"node_id":"PR_kwDOEHbxG87Jjrs8","html_url":"https://github.com/doldecomp/melee/pull/2268","diff_url":"https://github.com/doldecomp/melee/pull/2268.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/doldecomp/melee/pull/2268.patch","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/issues/2268","number":2268,"state":"closed","locked":false,"title":"Almost finish mngallery.c + misc matches","user":{"login":"dwilliams27","id":43834310,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQzODM0MzEw","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/43834310?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/dwilliams27","html_url":"https://github.com/dwilliams27","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dwilliams27/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dwilliams27/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dwilliams27/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dwilliams27/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dwilliams27/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dwilliams27/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dwilliams27/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dwilliams27/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dwilliams27/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"body":"This should be much higher quality than the 100 function match PR I submitted before. Apologies on that one, included some runs where some of the agent's tools were silently broken, so output varied in quality a lot.\r\n\r\nI think these should be good (especially mngallery.c). Let me know any issues you see, I'll incorporate feedback into next batch.\r\n\r\nAlso if you all have any clue on how to wrap up fn_802590C4 that would be amazing information to add. I had the AIs running a ton of experiments and even had them [disassemble and analyze MWCC itself](https://github.com/dwilliams27/gc-decomp/blob/main/docs/MWCC_COLORING_ANALYSIS.md), got close but couldn't close the gap. Fair warning some of the docs in that repo may contain some garbage, they were wrote by and for agents lol\r\n\r\nmngallery.c (9 new)                                                                                            \r\n1. mnGallery_8025896C\r\n2. mnGallery_80258A08\r\n3. mnGallery_80258BC4\r\n4. mnGallery_80258DBC\r\n5. fn_80258ED0\r\n6. mnGallery_802591BC\r\n7. mnGallery_80259604\r\n8. mnGallery_8025963C\r\n9. mnGallery_80259868\r\n10. fn_802590C4 (at like 95% fuzzy match, this one is super difficult to finish)\r\n\r\ngm_1601.c (4 new)\r\n1. gm_801636D8\r\n2. gm_80163838\r\n3. gm_80163A3C\r\n4. gm_80164430\r\n\r\ngrcorneria.c (1 new)\r\n1. grCorneria_801DEC94\r\n\r\nlbaudio_ax.c (3 new)\r\n1. lbAudioAx_800263E8\r\n2. lbAudioAx_80026510\r\n3. lbAudioAx_80026F2C","created_at":"2026-03-11T02:05:47Z","updated_at":"2026-03-11T05:13:01Z","closed_at":"2026-03-11T05:13:00Z","merged_at":"2026-03-11T05:13:00Z","merge_commit_sha":"07eb4ecd862fe9032683d49055ce4a5bbda510dd","assignees":[],"requested_reviewers":[],"requested_teams":[],"labels":[],"milestone":null,"draft":false,"commits_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2268/commits","review_comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2268/comments","review_comment_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/comments{/number}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/issues/2268/comments","statuses_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/statuses/6d67b8ddc1d485bf11c67fa64c5dc6b1d8be7f94","head":{"label":"dwilliams27:master","ref":"master","sha":"6d67b8ddc1d485bf11c67fa64c5dc6b1d8be7f94","user":{"login":"dwilliams27","id":43834310,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQzODM0MzEw","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/43834310?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/dwilliams27","html