omments{/number}","contents_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/contents/{+path}","compare_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/compare/{base}...{head}","merges_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/merges","archive_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/{archive_format}{/ref}","downloads_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/downloads","issues_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/issues{/number}","pulls_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls{/number}","milestones_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/milestones{/number}","notifications_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/notifications{?since,all,participating}","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/labels{/name}","releases_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/releases{/id}","deployments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/deployments","created_at":"2020-06-30T23:27:55Z","updated_at":"2026-06-01T22:58:14Z","pushed_at":"2026-06-01T22:58:08Z","git_url":"git://github.com/doldecomp/melee.git","ssh_url":"git@github.com:doldecomp/melee.git","clone_url":"https://github.com/doldecomp/melee.git","svn_url":"https://github.com/doldecomp/melee","homepage":null,"size":145408,"stargazers_count":901,"watchers_count":901,"language":"C","has_issues":true,"has_projects":true,"has_downloads":true,"has_wiki":true,"has_pages":true,"has_discussions":false,"forks_count":136,"mirror_url":null,"archived":false,"disabled":false,"open_issues_count":21,"license":null,"allow_forking":true,"is_template":false,"web_commit_signoff_required":false,"has_pull_requests":true,"pull_request_creation_policy":"all","topics":[],"visibility":"public","forks":136,"open_issues":21,"watchers":901,"default_branch":"master"}},"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2268"},"html":{"href":"https://github.com/doldecomp/melee/pull/2268"},"issue":{"href":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/issues/2268"},"comments":{"href":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/issues/2268/comments"},"review_comments":{"href":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2268/comments"},"review_comment":{"href":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/comments{/number}"},"commits":{"href":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2268/commits"},"statuses":{"href":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/statuses/6d67b8ddc1d485bf11c67fa64c5dc6b1d8be7f94"}},"author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","auto_merge":{"enabled_by":{"login":"ribbanya","id":5190964,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjUxOTA5NjQ=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5190964?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya","html_url":"https://github.com/ribbanya","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"merge_method":"squash","commit_title":"Almost finish mngallery.c + misc matches (#2268)","commit_message":"* Match mnGallery_8025896C, mnGallery_80258DBC, add stubs for remaining functions\n\n5/12 mngallery functions now matched (80258940, 8025896C, 80258D50, 80258DBC, 80259604).\nAdded includes, static var mnGallery_804D6C88, and stub markers for unmatched functions.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Match fn_80021FF8 in melee/lb/lbrefract.c\n\n* Match lbAudioAx_800263E8 in melee/lb/lbaudio_ax.c\n\n* Match grCorneria_801DEC94 in melee/gr/grcorneria.c\n\n* Match gm_801636D8 in melee/gm/gm_1601.c\n\n* mngallery: match 9/12 functions, add stubs for remaining 3\n\nMatched functions:\n- mnGallery_80258940, mnGallery_8025896C, mnGallery_80258BC4\n- mnGallery_80258D50, mnGallery_80258DBC, fn_80258ED0\n- mnGallery_802591BC, mnGallery_80259604, mnGallery_8025963C\n\nRemaining (3 functions):\n- mnGallery_80258A08 (93.7%)\n- mnGallery_80259868 (87.9%)\n- fn_802590C4 (38.3%)\n\nAdds required headers and mngallery.h type updates.\n\n* lbrefract: revert NOT_IMPLEMENTED stubs to stub markers\n\nThe headless agent replaced /// #function markers with NOT_IMPLEMENTED\nplaceholders for 4 unmatched functions. Revert to proper stub markers.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Improve mngallery.c: 80258A08 to 96%, 802590C4 to 82.3%\n\nmnGallery_80258A08: Reorder float declarations (zero, far, left, top,\nbottom, right) and use register keyword for zero initialization.\nImproves from 93.7% to 96.0%.\n\nfn_802590C4: Restructure loop with explicit store/ud copy pattern and\nzero=i assignment. Improves from 38.3% to 82.3%.\n\n* Improve mnGallery_80259868 to 89.5%\n\nReorder statement assignments (hovered_selection first, cooldown last)\nand declare arr before base to improve prologue scheduling.\nUp from 87.9%.\n\n* Match mnGallery_80258A08 at 100% (10/12 mngallery.c)\n\nUse #pragma opt_propagation off to prevent MWCC from eliminating\nthe near_val copy, forcing 7 FPR saves to match the target stack\nframe. Reorder float declarations (top, bottom, left, right) for\ncorrect register numbering.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Improve fn_802590C4 to 90.3% via declaration reorder\n\nExhaustive search of all 720 declaration permutations found\n(store, i, data, jobj, ud, zero) as optimal ordering.\nUp from 82.3%.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Improve mnGallery_80259868 to ~97% via statement reorder\n\nReorder struct field accesses to match canonical mn/ pattern:\ncooldown first, then prev_menu=cur_menu, then remaining fields,\nthen archive load. This produces lbzu (load-byte-with-update)\ninstead of addi+lbz, matching the target's peephole optimization.\nEliminates the extra mr r4,r0 instruction (98→97 insns).\n\nRemaining diff: 3-instruction scheduling swap at positions 25-27\n(sth/stb/addi reordered vs target). All other instructions match\nafter relocation masking.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Match mnGallery_80259868 at 100% (11/12 mngallery.c)\n\nPermuter found the fix: extract `arr + 6` into a local `new_var`\nbefore the state assignments. This changes register allocation\nenough to fix the instruction scheduling that was causing the\n3-instruction diff at positions 25-27.\n\nKey changes:\n- Add `void** new_var = arr + 6` before cooldown/menu assignments\n- Pass `new_var` instead of `arr + 6` to lbArchive_LoadSections\n- Reorder cur_menu/hovered_selection to match target\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Improve fn_802590C4 to 93.1% via pragma tuning (90.3% → 93.1%)\n\nUse #pragma optimization_level 2 + opt_strength_reduction on +\nopt_propagation off to get 62 instructions (matching target count)\nwith preserved register copy for zero = i. Remaining 11 diffs are\nregister encoding in loop setup — confirmed compiler floor via\n2880+ declaration order sweeps and deep MWCC RE.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* mngallery: improve fn_802590C4 match\n\n* Revert non-matching functions, recover grCorneria_801DEC94\n\n- Revert gm_8016260C to stub (51.5% match, not ready)\n- Revert lbrefract.c to upstream (had NOT_IMPLEMENTED stubs)\n- Recover grCorneria_801DEC94 (100% match) lost during merge\n- Revert grCorneria_801E0D30 (97.2%) and grCorneria_801E2D90 (91.7%) to stubs\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* grcorneria.h: only keep signature for matched grCorneria_801DEC94\n\nReset to upstream and only update the one function we matched.\nPrevious commit had extra signature changes for unmatched functions.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* grcorneria.c: remove extra static declarations from reverted functions\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* mngallery: include gobjobject header\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>"},"assignee":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"merged":true,"mergeable":null,"rebaseable":null,"mergeable_state":"unknown","merged_by":{"login":"ribbanya","id":5190964,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjUxOTA5NjQ=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5190964?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya","html_url":"https://github.com/ribbanya","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ribbanya/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"comments":2,"review_comments":0,"maintainer_can_modify":false,"commits":24,"additions":754,"deletions":68,"changed_files":8}